Tieng viet:
PACKAGE WebsocketController

    WebsocketController la noi cu ly du lieu realtime 2 chieu tu FE -> BE va nguoc lai.

    Du lieu realTime nay co the ap dung truc tiep cho nguoi dung truy cap truc tiep tren ung dung admin BFF
    hoac co the su dung cho nguoi dung truy cap tu nhieu ung dung khac thong qua 2 luong chinh la Upstream va
    Downstream cua Websocket. Trong do:

        1.  @MessageMapping(app-router)
            Luong Upstream gui tu FE ve cho BFF server

        2.  @SendTo(topic-router)
            Luong Downstream Broadcast phan hoi tu BFF cho FE

        3.  @SendToUser(user-router)
            Luong Downstream Private phan hoi tu BFF cho FE

Trong ngu canh la ung dung admin BFF, thi WebsocketController voi chuc nang quan ly phien ket noi socket la khong can thi
vi da duoc dinh nghia trong 2 class Component duoc giai thich tai Documentation theo duong dan:
    admin/src/main/java/ti/dabble/configurations/AuthSocket/documentation

